<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Maintenance Notification - IpTruck</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #ff9800;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .maintenance-status {
            background-color: #fbe9e7;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸ”§ Maintenance Notification</h1>
        <p>
            <%= maintenanceTitle %>
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>
            Dear <%= username %>,
        </p>
        
        <p>
            We would like to inform you that there will be a scheduled maintenance for your vehicle with registration number <%= vehicleRegNo %>.
        </p>

        <div class="maintenance-status">
            <h2>ðŸ›  Maintenance Details</h2>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= maintenanceDate %></p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= maintenanceTime %></p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= maintenanceLocation %></p>
            <p><strong>Estimated Duration:</strong> <%= maintenanceDuration %></p>
            <p><strong>Service Type:</strong> <%= serviceType %></p>
        </div>

        <p>
            Please ensure that your vehicle is available at the specified location and time for the service.
        </p>

        <p>
            If you have any questions or need to reschedule, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a> or call our customer service line.
        </p>

        <center>
            <a href="https://iptruck.com/maintenance/<%= maintenanceId %>" class="button">View Maintenance Details</a>
        </center>

        <p>
            Thank you for choosing IpTruck for your logistics needs.
        </p>

        <p>
            Best regards,<br>
            The IpTruck Maintenance Team
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2024 IpTruck. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You received this email because your vehicle is due for maintenance.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
